These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
House: cottage, palace, futuristic, townhouse
1. the cottage house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
3. the cottage house is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| House   | futuristic | palace | cottage | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, train, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Transport   | scooter | train | tram | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, begonia, orchid
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Flower   | begonia | dahlia | amaryllis | orchid |

 #################################

 
