1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |   3    |     4     |
| Birthday   | december | september | october | march |

